{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"93b74e52f5","title":"命令","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e077c9c9d6","index":0,"year":1937,"month":7,"day":14,"articleId":"93b74e52f5"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui1","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1913-1943卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui1a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"45ebb972a2","type":"title","text":"命令","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"93b74e52f5"},{"id":"ca516fc061","type":"paragraph","text":"总指挥、任政委、林校长、各方面军、各军团、各军、各师、各团及各军事学枚首长，同志们：","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"93b74e52f5"},{"id":"24ff99f1c6","type":"paragraph","text":"（甲）：","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"93b74e52f5"},{"id":"7eb05a0990","type":"paragraph","text":"日本大举向华北出兵，国家危急！廿九军正在抗战，国民政府已调派援军，全国救亡运动，正在奋起，我抗日红军有开赴前线，增援友军，并配合友军消灭野蛮日军之务。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"93b74e52f5"},{"id":"bb6d393346","type":"paragraph","text":"（乙）：","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"93b74e52f5"},{"id":"e7bb75f3a9","type":"paragraph","text":"令到即以军为单位，改组为国民革命军编制，同时增加抗日政治课程，对干部及兵员教授东西省及华北五省地理，教授日本现状．军事训练，着重雪地战斗，夜间动作，袭击战斗，防空救术，长途行军，无后方作战等项，各军事学校大体相同，照此办理。","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"93b74e52f5"},{"id":"19f700531a","type":"paragraph","text":"以上各项限十天完毕听候出动命令。","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"93b74e52f5"},{"id":"72973f8fff","type":"paragraph","text":"军委主席团","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"93b74e52f5"},{"id":"3a536c47b3","type":"paragraph","text":"（此命令对红军公开宣布，惟对日寇及汉奸分子严守秘密，不得疏忽。）","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"93b74e52f5"}],"page":{"id":"4ecde3e903","publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"93b74e52f5","start":310,"end":310}}}},"__N_SSG":true}